88
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:47,340
Uncle Erbai.

89
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:49,860
Be patient.

90
00:14:51,660 --> 00:14:53,140
Leave

91
00:14:53,580 --> 00:14:54,620
