266
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:26,460
These two new friends are the bodyguards of Bai.

267
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:27,300
That's not true!

268
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:28,100
Look at that guy

269
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,780
with a thick bowl haircut.

270
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:31,580
This is Jia Kezi.

271
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:33,620
This one who

272
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:36,900
