273
00:29:37,020 --> 00:29:38,220
His name is Li Jiale.

274
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:39,660
That's a lot to take in, right?

275
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:40,340
Let's hug again.

276
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:46,780
I haven't had enough.

277
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:49,460
Mr. Jiao.

278
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:51,820
I brought you out of the water.

279
00:29:58,220 --> 00:29:59,460
Is the exit in front of us?

280
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:02,860
Go further.

281
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:09,260
It's a dead end.

282
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,060
